oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Parasites and fly larvae in Poultry manure
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Nordentoft, Steen
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Farming Systems
Animal husbandry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: To test if larvae of Musca domestica added to chicken manure are able to eliminate or reduce the number of eggs and oocysts of pathogenic parasite species relevant to the poultry industry.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Nordentoft, Steen (2014) Parasites and fly larvae in Poultry manure. National Food Institute, Technical University of Denmark.
